726845f-a.title: Queens: Hampstead Avenue - 223rd Street
726845f-a.text:
Hempstead Avenue, at the S.N. corner of P23rd Street,
viewing westward and showing an old farmhouse occupying
the site. The property was owned by the estate of Dr. J.
Miller in 1891 and by Annie Shadill in 1909.
March 4, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
